				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">the rumor- a squad can man 3 prowlers, that same squad can man 5 vanguards. therefore, the NC can field more armor and are more effective dispite the firepower of the prowler.
<br />

<br />
the reality- man 5 prowlers anyway and pickup gunners. a pickup is more effective manning a gun then he is zerging with a cycler.
<br />

<br />
the response to reality- the gunner of the chaingun is more effective in a lightning or a reaver rather then sitting in the chaingunner spot.
<br />

<br />
the circle continues- it costs no certs to gun, there is no timer to gun.
<br />

<br />
and again- the prowler is slow, sluggish, huge, low armor, low firing arc, making it hard to hit or avoid anything. therefore making its paper firepower obsolete.
<br />

<br />
its a never ending cycle. that is why nothing can ever be in balance, its the same for every game out there. all you can hope for is a reasonable balance rather then an equal one. 
<br />

<br />
stats on paper are not real battle situations, real battle situations are unpredictable. since its unpredictable to predict a battle situation, balance must go by the stats on paper. however, stats on paper are not real battle situations, real battle situations are unpredictable. and on and on it goes.<br />_________________<br /><img src="http://www.soulcorp.com/sm/KAAOS/oaksilencer.png" border="0" /></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
